01:40.434 --> 01:43.804 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: An earlier
cessation of
hostilities failed after
numerous regime and

01:43.837 --> 01:45.472 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
