attacks targeting
the country's police and
military.

02:19.106 --> 02:24.177 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Philippine government has
agreed to an
indefinite cease-fire with
communist rebels.

02:24.211 --> 02:28.615 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's aimed at ending one of
Asia's longest-running
insurgencies, a conflict that's
killed at

02:28.648 --> 02:31.651 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
