hailed the agreement.

02:42.629 --> 02:49.102 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JESUS DUREZA, Representative of
the Philippine
Government: This is an historic
and unprecedented

02:49.136 --> 02:50.937 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
event.

02:50.971 --> 02:56.443 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
