off what we
have started a long time ago.

03:00.781 --> 03:04.418 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN:
Representatives from both
sides agreed to return to Oslo
in October

03:04.451 --> 03:06.787 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
for further negotiations.

03:06.820 --> 03:12.059 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
France's top administrative
court overturned
a controversial ban on the
so-called burkini

03:12.092 --> 03:13.860 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
