by Muslim
women has sparked a fierce
debate in France.

03:19.199 --> 03:22.536 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Martin Geissler of Independent
Television
News has our report from Paris.

03:22.569 --> 03:27.140 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARTIN GEISSLER: These were the
pictures that
divided France and shocked the
world beyond,

03:27.174 --> 03:32.112 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a Muslim woman forced by a group
of armed
policemen to remove her clothing
on a public

03:32.145 --> 03:33.880 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
beach.

03:33.914 --> 03:38.752 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
