04:10.250 --> 04:15.055 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
NICOLAS SARKOZY, French
President (through
translator): I support without
any hesitation

04:15.088 --> 04:19.192 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
