burkini to
preserve public order.

04:19.226 --> 04:24.531 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I ask for a law forbidding it on
the entire
territory of the republic.

04:24.564 --> 04:29.102 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARTIN GEISSLER: There was
little sign of
stress at the manmade beach on
the banks of

04:29.136 --> 04:35.008 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the sand today, Parisians
enjoying some late
summer sunshine, no burkinis to
be seen.

04:35.041 --> 04:37.077 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
