04:43.383 --> 04:44.651 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
That's why it offends people."

04:44.684 --> 04:48.421 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
WOMAN: We live in a free
country, so they
do what they want.

04:48.455 --> 04:53.026 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If they want to wear something
like this,
it's not...

04:53.059 --> 04:54.728 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MAN: It's no problem.

04:54.761 --> 04:56.496 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
WOMAN: Yes.

04:56.530 --> 04:59.900 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARTIN GEISSLER: These are
extreme times in
France, and many here believe
they require

04:59.933 --> 05:01.635 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
extreme measures.

05:01.668 --> 05:06.473 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
