05:16.516 --> 05:19.352 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The human
rights lawyer
fighting the ban said that while
today's ruling

05:19.386 --> 05:24.224 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
