Katbi to flee her home country
four years

38:22.567 --> 38:24.235 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
ago.

38:24.269 --> 38:28.740 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now she runs a center in Amman,
Jordan, that
cares for refugees fleeing from
Syria.

38:28.773 --> 38:31.476 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
They're recovering from the
trauma of war.

38:31.509 --> 38:37.182 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Souriyat Across Borders is a
home away from
home for refugees suffering from
both physical

38:37.215 --> 38:39.684 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
