at the center, all free of
charge.

38:44.756 --> 38:49.127 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NISREEN KHAZNA KATBI, Souriyat
Across Borders:
This is where they have their
physical therapy

38:49.160 --> 38:50.929 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
training.

38:50.962 --> 38:54.999 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LACY JANE ROBERTS: Nisreen and
