39:11.082 --> 39:18.756 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NISREEN KHAZNA KATBI: They faced
some frightening
situations, like the bombings,
the killing,

39:18.790 --> 39:22.060 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
