severe injuries.

39:22.093 --> 39:27.065 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LACY JANE ROBERTS: But Souriyat
Across Borders
has no full-time mental health
professionals

39:27.098 --> 39:28.733 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
on staff.

39:28.766 --> 39:32.670 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
So, when a mental health
training project
run by a group of
California-based doctors

39:32.704 --> 39:36.341 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
came to Amman, Nisreen signed
up.

39:36.374 --> 39:44.782 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Dr. Saad Shakir leads CPR, or
Care Program
for Refugees.

39:44.816 --> 39:49.988 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
At first, CPR's goal was to give
