a positive

40:12.944 --> 40:14.746 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
way.

40:14.779 --> 40:19.050 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LACY JANE ROBERTS: Dr. Atef
