health workers to apply group
therapy.

41:00.892 --> 41:05.997 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
At their field clinic in the
Zaatari refugee
camp, the counselors with the
Noor Al-Hussein

41:06.030 --> 41:09.634 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Foundation try to see as many
people as possible
