42:02.553 --> 42:04.322 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

42:04.355 --> 42:07.558 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWENOLA GHANES, Doctors Without
Borders: On
a psychological point of view,
there is no

42:07.592 --> 42:08.793 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
rules.

42:08.826 --> 42:11.362 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It's not a mathematical
equation.

42:11.396 --> 42:18.436 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Most of the people will develop
symptoms such
as depression or anxiety
disorder, and a small

42:18.469 --> 42:20.171 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
