be affected by the trauma of
war.

42:25.543 --> 42:28.279 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Talha Al-Ali is a pediatric
counselor.

42:28.312 --> 42:31.282 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
