rebuild trust.

42:31.315 --> 42:33.084 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

42:33.117 --> 42:34.452 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
TALHA AL-ALI, Pediatric
Counselor: They start
at the beginning to have the
small social

42:34.485 --> 42:37.755 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
networks while playing or while
doing activities
together.

42:37.789 --> 42:42.827 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Like, a child will start to
adapt again with
building relationships, and
especially to

42:42.860 --> 42:44.829 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
