42:52.003 --> 42:55.973 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LACY JANE ROBERTS: After the
training, Nisreen
Katbi says she will be able to
provide better

42:56.007 --> 42:57.775 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
care for the patient-residents.

42:57.809 --> 43:05.049 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NISREEN KHAZNA KATBI: I have
learned how to
deal with certain cases, like if
he is having

43:05.082 --> 43:12.023 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
