aggressive
in a certain way or depressed.

43:12.056 --> 43:16.928 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LACY JANE ROBERTS: Dr. Ghanes
agrees that,
while this kind of training is
useful, much

43:16.961 --> 43:18.129 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
