43:18.162 --> 43:19.163 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

43:19.197 --> 43:20.832 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWENOLA GHANES: It's useful, but
it's not
enough.

43:20.865 --> 43:25.903 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
